00:01:50.520 --> 00:01:54.220
Heijara and Matu own a fashion shop here in the capital city.

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:33.580
The girls want to expand their business so they plan to venture further into the country.

00:02:33.940 --> 00:02:37.640
They want to see what's on offer and what's on demand in and around the ancient capital.

00:02:37.880 --> 00:02:49.020
[Music]

00:02:49.200 --> 00:02:53.480
Mauritania has been known for centuries in the Arab world as the land of Chinguetti.

00:02:53.480 --> 00:02:56.720
One of the ancient cities Muslims consider sacred.

00:02:59.300 --> 00:03:04.420
The United Nations ranks Mauritania as one of the world's least developed countries.

00:03:05.760 --> 00:03:10.820
The Sahara desert takes up most of the country which is about twice the size of France

00:03:11.540 --> 00:03:17.800
But it's population is only around 3 million people. That's less than Paris and its suburbs.

00:03:18.600 --> 00:03:24.440
Life is hard here in this isolated society where old traditions are rigidly maintained.

00:04:01.900 --> 00:05:20.600
[Music]

00:07:52.120 --> 00:08:00.560
[Music]

00:08:00.560 --> 00:08:07.340
As beauties from the capital Heijara and Matu are honored guests at this party where a concert will be the main event.

00:08:07.620 --> 00:08:08.120
This is where people go to see and be seen.

00:08:08.120 --> 00:09:57.620
[Music]

00:10:07.480 --> 00:10:57.100
[Music]

