00:13:45.840 --> 00:13:59.520
[Music]

00:15:31.400 --> 00:15:40.640
There are no fashion magazines in Mauritania, but girls are able to tune into what's in Vogue around the world using the internet.

00:15:54.100 --> 00:17:17.540
[Music]

00:20:29.580 --> 00:21:01.520
[Music]

00:21:01.700 --> 00:21:05.660
This is Heijara and Matu's first time in the ancient city of Chinguetti.

00:21:05.660 --> 00:21:10.320
[Music]

00:21:10.420 --> 00:21:14.000
They're enjoying the opportunity to go shopping.

00:21:49.980 --> 00:21:58.400
[Laughter]

