[Music]

00:23:11.820 --> 00:23:15.880
Our heroines are back with their daughters in Nouakchott.

00:23:17.080 --> 00:23:23.140
They claim to have gained a couple of kilos in weight during this trip, so it's time for a day of fasting.

00:24:04.380 --> 00:24:08.020
